caption: Hey friends! 🌞 Today I captured a fresh vibe in the heart of the city—under the neon‑lit sky of the downtown plaza, I wore my coral‑pink flower sundress, and let the sun play on my skin. I’m standing with my hand on my hip, the camera’s low angle catching the texture of my hair and the crisp light. Can't wait to share the rest of this journey! #fashion #sundress #travel #lifestyle
